    Selector: lightning-output-field Represents the lightning-output-field Lightning web component. Get the output field's label text. Get the string value of the name, text, phone, rich text, lookup, email, number, location, url, or address based on the component type. , created from JSON resources/utam/lightning/outputField.utam.json
